## Raw simulator captures for App Store / preview work. These are large
## (~5 MB per shot × 16 shots ≈ 50 MB) and bloat the repo for no
## runtime / deploy benefit. The web-optimized JPEGs at web/manual-images/
## (~50 KB each) are what the manual + Pages actually serve; the originals
## can always be regenerated with scripts/screenshot.sh.
screenshots/

## Claude Code — keep shared launch + settings, but settings.local.json
## is per-machine (simulator IDs, personal paths, accumulated allowlists)
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/cache/

